Building APR trunk in VC 6 using the Win9X Debug build results in an compile error at line 428.  The 
expression there is clearly missing a closing semi-colon.  The semi-colon was there in 1.2.12.

Index: file_io/win32/open.c
===============================================================
====
--- file_io/win32/open.c	(revision 616652)
+++ file_io/win32/open.c	(working copy)
@@ -424,7 +424,7 @@
         handle = CreateFileA(fname, oflags, sharemode,
                              NULL, createflags, attributes, 0);
         /* This feature is not supported on this platform. */
-        flag &= ~APR_SENDFILE_ENABLED
+        flag &= ~APR_SENDFILE_ENABLED;
     }
 #endif
     if (handle == INVALID_HANDLE_VALUE) {
